## Governance overview

The Crisis Management Team (CMT) is activated by severity, not by emergency type. When a situation matches a scenario in the activation guide, the crisis lead declares the level and convenes the listed roles. Each role executes their section in the playbook — there is no separate procedure per emergency type.

